<div id="attachment_246905" style="width: 1930px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246905" class="wp-image-246905 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sanchez-7.jpg" alt="a ballpoint pen drawing of a ghostly white horse in a dark stable in a small sketchbook" width="1920" height="1280" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sanchez-7.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sanchez-7-640x427.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sanchez-7-960x640.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sanchez-7-1536x1024.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
