</div>
<div id="attachment_246295" style="width: 1930px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246295" class="wp-image-246295 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/verginer-9.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1281" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/verginer-9.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/verginer-9-640x427.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/verginer-9-960x641.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/verginer-9-1536x1025.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
<p id="caption-attachment-246295" class="wp-caption-text">“The pink bear” (2022), lindenwood and acrylic, 85 x 225 x 90 centimeters</p>
</div>
<div id="attachment_246290" style="width: 1290px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246290" class="wp-image-246290 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/verginer-4.jpeg" alt="" width="1280" height="1920" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/verginer-4.jpeg 1280w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/verginer-4-640x960.jpeg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/verginer-4-960x1440.jpeg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/verginer-4-1024x1536.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px"></p>
